      üìú Menu - <span id="selectedTable">Ch·ªçn b√†n</span>
    </h3>
    <div class="table-responsive">
      <table class="table table-bordered">
        <thead class="table-dark">
          <tr>
            <th>Lo·∫°i m√≥n</th>
